song_lyrics: Jay Shrī Sahajānand sukhad Swāmī... jay 1
Raṭat dashshat vadan nigam agam sadā,
Jaysi tvam namat sur shīsh nāmī;
Jaysi tvam bhajat muni bhakta nishkāmjan,
Kāl māyā purush rachat brahmānḍ bahu,
Hot pālan pralay tav bhrukuṭī bhang karī,
Jay Shrī Sarveshvar aham namāmi... jay 3
Jay Shrī Kamalāpati jay Shrī Naishthik jati,
Jay Shrī Parameshwar tav charaṇ sharaṇ me,
title: Jay Shrī Nārāyaṇ sarvakāraṇ sadā
